{"data": {"__GLOBAL": {"_ATTACH_BASE_VIEW": "img.nga.178.com/attachments"}, "__U": {"150058": {"uid": 150058, "username": "UID:150058", "credit": 135537218, "medal": "272,207,157,92", "reputation": "28_30,61_0,147_775,130_10", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 73, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1123989606, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 41408, "rvrc": 29, "money": 90765, "thisvisit": 1783502750, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135537218, "buffs": {"131": [[1618226, 131, 67252859, 150058, 1783306372, 1783565572, 7, 0], [1684687, 131, 60009658, 150058, 1783408184, 1783667384, 47, 0]]}}, "66989363": {"uid": 66989363, "username": "UID:66989363", "credit": 135275008, "medal": null, "reputation": "147_-300", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1762774156, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 2793, "rvrc": 10, "money": 0, "thisvisit": 1783464929, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135275008}, "__GROUPS": {"73": ["学徒", 360672, 73], "39": ["学徒", 98528, 39]}, "__MEDALS": {"272": ["272.gif", "棒棒糖", "叔叔请你吃棒棒糖", 272], "207": ["207.gif", "爆竹声中旧岁除", "一支红杏出墙来", 207], "157": ["157.gif", "王者之剑", "王者之剑活动纪念", 157], "92": ["92.gif", "小心死亡之翼-", "2011年大灾变开服纪念", 92]}, "__REPUTATIONS": {"147": {"150058": 775, "66989363": -300, "0": "大时代"}}}, "__R": [{"pid": 873480012, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 69, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-30 22:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873479647,45974302,8547]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=63986423]ddyoo321[/uid] (2026-06-30 22:28):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大晚上好，想请教一个关于智驾方面的问题，前些时候L3L4自动驾驶的标准定稿，结合笛子提前一年兜底，理应是个行业催化性事件，为什么智驾板块一点动静都没有，甚至港股相关标的还破位下杀。[/quote]<br/>法律法规就是那个质变的坎", "lou": 3520, "content_length": 29, "reply_to": 873479647, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782830004}, {"pid": 873536187, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 205, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 12:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "一切以盘面验证逻辑预判<br/><br/>现在就是培养习惯的时候 让大家一点点的认错<br/>让进来的资金不买科技的变成买科技  买科技的变成抱科技  抱科技的变成抱科技指数  抱科技指数的变成抱科技基金 最后完全对市场脱敏<br/>这里不是说科技是不是马上大顶，而是最后进去的钱带不出来了。<br/>我的逻辑和操作都是延续的  市场会验证", "lou": 3521, "content_length": 270, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782879777}, {"pid": 873536614, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 105, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 12:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873536449,45974302,8590]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143809]Rzzz二号机[/uid] (2026-07-01 12:25):[/b]<br/><br/>意思是铁盒还能涨？[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>意思是当一个题材类型最赚钱的效应在板块指数的时候 你做不了超额", "lou": 3522, "content_length": 65, "reply_to": 873536449, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782879996}, {"pid": 873537364, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 66, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 12:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873537104,45974302,8591]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143809]Rzzz二号机[/uid] (2026-07-01 12:30):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:哭笑]那不还是想吃不如买指数  [del]不是 原来已经到这一步了吗[/del][/quote]<br/>重点是你会不会被对盘面脱敏", "lou": 3523, "content_length": 31, "reply_to": 873537104, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782880363}, {"pid": 873538070, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 150, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 12:38", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873537658,45974302,8591]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39810331]a471428019[/uid] (2026-07-01 12:35):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大今天这是什么操作老登集体反弹，好多涨停，[/quote]<br/>我已经说了  现在没有主力在猛猛干科技了 <br/>大家都是腾出利润 去做各种中报方向<br/>不管是金融 新能源 甚至是药或者是其他超跌方向等等 都差不多<br/>之前我已经说得很明确了我觉得 是非常白的大白话<br/>我的科技都是持仓等结束的状态。", "lou": 3524, "content_length": 201, "reply_to": 873537658, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782880732}, {"pid": 873539176, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 67, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 12:49", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873538997,45974302,8592]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1241533]嘻哈小树苗[/uid] (2026-07-01 12:48):[/b]<br/><br/>光存这种明牌的大科技中报意思是提前做完了吗，其实我也一直从人性的角度觉得近期一堆散户埋伏光存的中报，主力怎么能让他们这么轻松的挣钱，哪怕是小钱，肯定不能太让他们如愿啊[/quote]<br/>都一样的啊。。。这边只是因为缺了港股通所以更弱一点啊。。。<br/>今天港股休市啊大哥们。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br/><br/><br/>无奈[s:ac:冷]", "lou": 3525, "content_length": 123, "reply_to": 873538997, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782881399}, {"pid": 873541465, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 70, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 13:12", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873541125,45974302,8595]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=37585733]j74587458[/uid] (2026-07-01 13:09):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大说7月做aidi7月就第一天就拉起来了，真的牛逼[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>所以比我提前有什么意思呢。", "lou": 3526, "content_length": 31, "reply_to": 873541125, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782882763}, {"pid": 873541564, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 60, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 13:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873541407,45974302,8595]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67225621]TeresaHu-[/uid] (2026-07-01 13:12):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大下午好，我有个问题特别想请教一下，油运板块尤其是招商轮船这种史无前例的12连跌，然后暴力反弹50%，再暴力A杀，这种一般是什么手法什么操作，百思不得其解，我实在问人无路，看看狼大能不能翻翻牌子帮我解一下惑，不胜感激。[/quote]<br/>我不会这种  我只能说我[color=red]之前[/color]说过 战争相关板块我不做了 并且指出中石油那种大顶又是一个五年起步。", "lou": 3527, "content_length": 89, "reply_to": 873541407, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782882820}, {"pid": 873542771, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 136, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 13:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873542497,45974302,8597]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=63445573]sds2332[/uid] (2026-07-01 13:22):[/b]<br/><br/>确实对科技有点脱敏了，外面天天跌，我猛涨，人已经有点膨胀了[/quote]<br/>我左芯片 右存储 光模块在胸口 材料在背后 人挡杀人 佛挡杀佛<br/><br/>是这样吧？", "lou": 3528, "content_length": 67, "reply_to": 873542497, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782883521}, {"pid": 873543159, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 95, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 13:28", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873542880,45974302,8598]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=952299]混帐咿呀[/uid] (2026-07-01 13:26):[/b]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202607/01/jmQ53-e66jZdT1kShs-12d.jpg[/img]<br/>拿了很久了，今早受不了卖了[s:ac:blink][/quote]<br/><br/>我还蛮佩服你们的 我说下半年看AIDC建设<br/>然后你在7月第一天卖掉<br/>[s:ac:赞同]", "lou": 3529, "content_length": 60, "reply_to": 873542880, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782883735}, {"pid": 873543520, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 55, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 13:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873543434,45974302,8599]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65664557]维拉帕米不是米[/uid] (2026-07-01 13:31):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，个股也可以按照打破下跌趋势的第二个红k打满嘛[s:ac:喘][/quote]<br/>不能", "lou": 3530, "content_length": 9, "reply_to": 873543434, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782883938}, {"pid": 873544128, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 138, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 13:37", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873543596,45974302,8600]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60916468]灰兔尾[/uid] (2026-07-01 13:32):[/b]<br/><br/>今天打了个板[s:ac:茶]好久没打板了，刺激[/quote]<br/>厉害  我说下半年开始AIDC 然后你们7月1日打板<br/><br/>短短一天内出现多种极端神操作。。。。", "lou": 3531, "content_length": 81, "reply_to": 873543596, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782884256}, {"pid": 873547448, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 107, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 14:05", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873547099,45974302,8609]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143809]Rzzz二号机[/uid] (2026-07-01 14:02):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 我问你个问题 你看方不方便回复<br/><br/>机构们是不是约好了暗号？  某个股票+5以上兄弟们就开砸？[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>之前不是说了么  资金大部分都按特定标号做网格  不管是日内+-5的幅度 或者是 各种线 黄金分割等 <br/>这就是为什么要观察个股资金盘口的原因  更多就是你自己看适不适合自己的操作模式<br/>如果一个票 他涨 但是不跟我的线 那就不适合我。我就不做 <br/>找共性。", "lou": 3532, "content_length": 220, "reply_to": 873547099, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782885940}, {"pid": 873547965, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 91, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 14:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873547674,45974302,8610]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143809]Rzzz二号机[/uid] (2026-07-01 14:07):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:哭笑]我指的不是单个票  我指的是单个票+6  开砸大盘[/quote]<br/>我知道你的意思的 中兴 <br/>不是的。<br/>我只是告诉你 以前茅台曾经有过这种地位<br/>现在是中继 但是中继他的日内波动只要在-7%内就没事。", "lou": 3533, "content_length": 118, "reply_to": 873547674, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782886207}, {"pid": 873548040, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 44, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 14:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873547931,45974302,8610]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67157410]c471167449[/uid] (2026-07-01 14:09):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大请教下，那既然资金比如+5就要砸，那谁去把票拉升到+5呢，总不能散户拉升的吧。。。[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>一个票里就一家资金?", "lou": 3534, "content_length": 24, "reply_to": 873547931, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782886240}, {"pid": 873548388, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 66, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 14:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873548283,45974302,8611]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143809]Rzzz二号机[/uid] (2026-07-01 14:12):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:哭笑]这才是焚决   但是今天中际波动-8了[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>-7% 那就是+- 14%", "lou": 3535, "content_length": 19, "reply_to": 873548283, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782886398}, {"pid": 873548809, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 75, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 14:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873548358,45974302,8611]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66997442]CyberFluxMaster[/uid] (2026-07-01 14:13):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，今天港股休息都有这么大量，要怎么解释呢？[/quote]<br/>大量是因为场外资金进场之后疯狂操作。。。很多资金在这里碰到大波动就很急躁了。一天恨不得操作300次<br/>你科技跌一点就补一下。你补一下机构资金就换到别的方向一点 <br/>增量不就来了", "lou": 3536, "content_length": 168, "reply_to": 873548358, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782886595}, {"pid": 873549537, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 55, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 14:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873549100,45974302,8612]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143809]Rzzz二号机[/uid] (2026-07-01 14:18):[/b]<br/><br/>我稍微有点好奇 哪来的这么多增量资金[s:ac:喷]  上周涨的也不多啊[/quote]<br/>指数上来了啊 怎么不多<br/>4000都涨到4100了 <br/>自从三天站稳后你没发现增量的时间更多了么 因为急了", "lou": 3537, "content_length": 89, "reply_to": 873549100, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782886928}, {"pid": 873549665, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 73, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 14:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873549390,45974302,8613]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65490615]子午卯酉甲乙丙丁[/uid] (2026-07-01 14:20):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，有个疑问就是最后一波毕业照是几个上半年热门板块(光 存 导 算)一起照毕业照，还是只有最后一波极致抱团的导独自照相呢？[/quote]<br/>抱团哪有同一天毕业照的 <br/>肯定是一个出现大批量负反馈 然后带崩其他的<br/>所以我为什么说我被动止盈都设置好了", "lou": 3538, "content_length": 101, "reply_to": 873549390, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782886995}, {"pid": 873552262, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 199, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-01 14:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873552114,45974302,8617]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67040883]Passule[/uid] (2026-07-01 14:42):[/b]<br/><br/>说了科技会死，都不信，现在狼大也说了，该信了吧？[/quote]<br/>我什么时候说科技会死了？", "lou": 3539, "content_length": 29, "reply_to": 873552114, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782888229}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 4, "replies": 182741, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1783518685, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "xenoblade4", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1783518976, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 7, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,654677,39235785,66063392,39314790,67071606,66251279,42126891,61602239,4785041,42995612,67024871,62241578,64199867,11586486,5641907,66685489,66633842,65208818,42941765,,42964685,42181525,14317962,67086252,34699482,62593385,67000864,64005788,62799978,60424140,42468630,61560061,67096060,61021164,67102441,63220970,19312329,60694817,67086969,67061200,60701305,66937546,62357329,41746951,60027718,,39248719,62403348,40776497,67088120,66875016,64268963,1459804,67062343,12177085,38702942,1383368,67093370,66885146,40024017,63922791,67095295,66895557,64571355,62824316,5495109,38806682,67122547,67137453,67078475,,38110681,66618696,64658121,67085304,38883076,67132556,67126715,62653482,67128658,64731349,67105996,65464857,67143142,67118412,36620789,62234787,67115759,67136133,2062702,4627122,67095345,67145169,67105952,67054948,67085379,66758380,43207490,37784933,19483255,34874814,37791497,14884234,64997287,63841614,8555597,67098132,62368609,39205700,42258905,61649350,122